ome</a></li><li id="menu-item-62082" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-62082"><a href="/chi-siamo-autori/">Chi siamo</a></li><li id="menu-item-61925" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category current-post-ancestor current-menu-parent current-post-parent menu-item-has-children menu-item-61925"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/recensioni/">Opera</a><ul class="sub-menu"><li id="menu-item-65488" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-65488"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/senza-categoria/">Foreign Readers</a></li></ul></li><li id="menu-item-61927" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-61927"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/concerti/">Concerti</a></li><li id="menu-item-61930" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-61930"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/danza/">Danza</a></li><li id="menu-item-61933" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-61933"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/link/">Indirizzi utili</a></li><li id="menu-item-61928" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-61928"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/interviste/">Interviste</a></li><li id="menu-item-61938" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-has-children menu-item-61938"><a href="#">Media</a><ul class="sub-menu"><li id="menu-item-61940" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-61940"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/cd-e-dvd/">Cd e Dvd</a></li><li id="menu-item-61941" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-61941"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/libreria/">Libreria</a></li><li id="menu-item-61939" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-61939"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/video-dalla-rete/">Video dalla rete</a></li></ul></li><li id="menu-item-61926" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-has-children menu-item-61926"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/news-ed-eventi/">News</a><ul class="sub-menu"><li id="menu-item-61934" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-61934"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/tv-e-radio/">Lirica in Tv</a></li></ul></li><li id="menu-item-61935" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-has-children menu-item-61935"><a href="#">Rubriche</a><ul class="sub-menu"><li id="menu-item-62011" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-62011"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/album-dei-ricordi/">Album dei ricordi</a></li><li id="menu-item-61931" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-61931"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/approfondimenti/">Approfondimenti</a></li><li id="menu-item-62012" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-62012"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/maria-callas/">Maria Callas</a></li><li id="menu-item-75734" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-75734"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/ludvig-van-beethoven-2/">Ludvig Van Beethoven</a></li><li id="menu-item-75733" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-75733"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/christoph-willibald-gluck/">Christoph Willibald Gluck</a></li><li id="menu-item-75735" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-75735"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/pietro-mascagni/">Pietro Mascagni</a></li><li id="menu-item-75736" class